    "form_header_text": "Congresswoman Luz Rivas FY27 Programmatic or Language Request",
    "form_instructions_text": "Please submit all request by Friday, March 6, 2026, 6:00 PM PT. One fundamental duty of the United Sates Congress is the appropriations process: the annual allocation of funds for federal discretionary programs that support everything from infrastructure projects, that put millions of Americans to work to nutrition assistance for low-income communities. Congresswoman Rivas wants to hear from the people of the San Fernando Valley about priorities that are most important for the district. The form below provides individuals and organizations with an opportunity to request congressional appropriations. Important note: All appropriations requests must comply with the Rules of the United States House of Representatives and federal law. All requests must be submitted through the form below to be considered. Please submit each appropriations request individually. Submissions not requested individually will not be considered. Questions about specific programs or language should be emailed to Rivas.Appropriations@mail.house.gov. Please note, this form is only for programmatic or language requests. For Community Project Funding information, please visit https://rivas.house.gov/appropriations.",
